  lines:
  - speakerName: Dario_OfDuty23
    text: "\u201C\xBF\xBF\xBFEl adblock???\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: -5629520258137542616, guid: 57b0ed940a3b7124b9e8d8312675581a, type: 3}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CEstuve limpiando y se me olvido ponerlo\u201D "
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: "\u201C\xBFEn serio? \xBF\xBFtanto era??\u201D\r\n"
    portrait: {fileID: 3964466543063010452, guid: b8d978cc7267f574e8faf94b712bce6e, type: 3}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CJa, ja, ja, ja, ja, \xA1Cu\xE1nto \xE9xito tienes con las mujeres!\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 770964363518036162, guid: 7e190e13ae52c134ba01ddbda9ad2217, type: 3}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CUff, a ver qu\xE9 podemos ver y os callais un poquito\u201D\r\n"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CYo quiero Nyan Sugar Neko Girls\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: -5538810942529525774, guid: a33738f2fe3bd9f41bb3279fa1a5f8a6, type: 3}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CEso es basura, pon How I became the lord of the dungeon\""
    portrait: {fileID: -5629520258137542616, guid: 57b0ed940a3b7124b9e8d8312675581a, type: 3}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: "\"C\xF3mo se nota que sois t\xEDos, pon algo decente por favor\""
    portrait: {fileID: -5629520258137542616, guid: 57b0ed940a3b7124b9e8d8312675581a, type: 3}
  - speakerName: 
    text: Voy a acabar hacinedo lo que quiera...
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  choices: []
